Ụlọ Ahịa na Ụlọ Ọrụ Lagos bụ ụlọ ọrụ na-enweghị uru ego na mpaghara Lagos nke na-akwalite, na-akwado ma ọ bụ na-emegide usoro iwu ma ọ bụ ihe ndị ọzọ na-emetụta azụmahịa, ụlọ ọrụ, azụmahịa na ọrụ ugbo yana ịnọchite anya echiche nke ndị azụmaahịa Lagos na ihe ndị dị n'elu karịsịa, na akụ na ụba n'ozuzu ya
Ọ na-etu ọnụ ihe karịrị ndị otu otu puku na narị ise.
E hiwere ya na Disemba 5, 1888, e debanyere aha ya n'afọ 1950 dị ka òtù na-enweghị uru, Limited by Guarantee n'okpuru Iwu Ụlọ Ọrụ nke afọ 1948
Ụlọ Ahịa Lagos bụ ụlọ ahịa ọsụ ụzọ na Naịjirịa.
Nnukwu ụlọ Commerce House nke nwere ọfịs ya dị na Victoria Island, ebe ọtụtụ ụlọ ọrụ Naijiria nwere isi ụlọ ọrụ mba ha.

Ụlọ ọrụ Lagos Chamber of Commerce & Industry weputara Chamber Awards na 2014 iji mata, kwalite ma mee emume ụlọ ọrụ onwe na nke ọha na eze na-arụ ọrụ na Naịjirịa maka omume azụmaahịa kachasị mma, uto site na ihe ọhụrụ, nkwado azụmaahịa na mmetụta dị mma na ndị mmadụ / ọha mmadụ.

Ihe nrite ahụ gosipụtara ụlọ ọrụ ndị dị na ụlọ ọrụ ndị a - Banking, Insurance, Pension Management, E-Payment, Education, Telecoms, Professional Services, Healthcare, Oil & Gas, Manufacturing, Trade / Retail Trade, Building & Construction na SMEs.

Maka ihe nrite nke afọ 2015, Beat 99.9 FM on-air personality, Olisa Adibua na Rhythm 93.7 FM on- air personality & celebrity vlogger, a họọrọ Toke Makinwa dị ka ndị ọbịa nke afọ 2015 Lagos Chambers of Commerce & Industry (LCCI) Awards.
A maara Lagos Chamber of Commerce & Industry nke ọma maka Lagos International Trade Fair nke a malitere n'afọ 1977
A na-ekwu na ọ bụ nnukwu ngosi azụmahịa na mpaghara West Africa ma na-adọta ndị na-etinye ego site n'akụkụ ndị ọzọ nke ụwa
[citation needed]  ngosi azụmahịa ahụ na-eme na Tafawa Balewa Square, Onikan, Lagos Island.
N'ọnwa Ọktoba afọ 2014, ụlọ ọrụ azụmahịa Lagos kpughere 2face Idibia, Brymo, Vector na Kunle Afolayan dị ka ndị nnọchi anya
A kpughere ndị na-eme ihe ntụrụndụ n'oge emume dị iche iche na Commerce House, nke dị na Idowu Taylor Street na Victoria Island, Lagos.
